snippet.title: Cartel Tycoon Live Action Trailer | Leaving Early Access on July 26
snippet.description:
Cartel Tycoon is leaving Early Access on July 26! Watch the live-action trailer now to feel what it's like to be a Capo.

Cartel Tycoon is a survival business sim inspired by the ‘80s narco trade. Expand and conquer, fight off rival cartels and evade the authorities. Earn people's loyalty and strive to overcome the doomed fate of a power-hungry drug lord.

Buy the game now to receive Early Access rewards! 

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1220140/Cartel_Tycoon/

https://discord.gg/CartelTycoon
https://twitter.com/CartelTycoon
https://www.facebook.com/CartelTycoon/
https://www.instagram.com/carteltycoon/

#carteltycoon #tinybuild #trailer #liveaction #moonmoose
